{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256711, "create_time": 1656232085, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re : 如果能来清华计算机只需要跟父母将目前贵系计算机本科毕业年薪六七十万就好了", "timestamp": 1656232085}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256712, "create_time": 1656232097, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "清华数学物理还行吧...我们那届有两个非竞赛生上了，现在也要保研了", "timestamp": 1656232097}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256713, "create_time": 1656232110, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "小镇做题家呗，cz之前也是这么想的，挺无解的", "timestamp": 1656232110}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256714, "create_time": 1656232125, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "如果不能来清华，北大未尝不是更好的选择，你的想法也不一定是正确的", "timestamp": 1656232125}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256715, "create_time": 1656232133, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "一个去高金，一个可能是去经管", "timestamp": 1656232133}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256717, "create_time": 1656232143, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 同意Alice，直接告诉他们各个专业的工资差距", "timestamp": 1656232143}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256719, "create_time": 1656232204, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "本科就有六七十了吗，害怕", "timestamp": 1656232204}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256720, "create_time": 1656232253, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1