: false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256759, "create_time": 1656232954, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Dave: 搞系统的真的这个价算少的", "timestamp": 1656232954}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256764, "create_time": 1656233067, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 我是网络博，网络的人虽然少，但网络一直都很好找工作，待遇一直不差；我现在也在参加华为提前批面试，已经进行到第三轮了，但能给200+的也是属于有sigcomm傍身的，数量很少", "timestamp": 1656233067}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256767, "create_time": 1656233177, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 我现在有另一家已经到手的offer，只能给到150；做系统的拿到200+也非常少", "timestamp": 1656233177}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256770, "create_time": 1656233226, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Dave: 恩，预计你可以拿到150？35岁危机如何度过？", "timestamp": 1656233226}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256771, "create_time": 1656233301, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Hans: 如果去华为，博士应该没有35岁危机，倒是有45岁危机；另，我150的offer不是互联网公司开的", "timestamp": 1656233301}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256776, "create_time": 1656233382, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Dave: 45岁差不多能赚到一两千万至少吧，整个退休，过田园生活去", "timestamp": 1656233382}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256786, "create_time": 1656233550, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Hans: 华为内部的退休年龄就是45，除非升上去了；但是就算年薪200W，税后也才120+，财富积累不容易啊", "timestamp": 1656233550}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 256810, "create_time": 1656234213, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "这么看来贵系博好香，不